  "title": "Warehouse Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Marine Logistics Hiring Warehouse Assistant</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p>\n<p>· To perform data entry in Cargowise system for inbound and outbound shipments</p>\n<p>. Communicate effectively with team members to ensure data accuracy</p>\n<p>· Update daily inventory report</p>\n<p>· Weekly/monthly stock count and random stock check, to ensure inventory accuracy for warehouse</p>\n<p>· Liaise with supplier and customer</p>\n<p>· To perform other ad-hoc duties as assigned by the superior</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>· “O” Level or equivalent.</p>\n<p>· Proficient in MS Office (Word, Excel, Outlook).</p>\n<p>· Fresh graduateor minimum 1 year warehouse experience</p>\n<p>· Able to work independent</p>\n<p>· Basic command over English (both verbal and written)</p>\n<p>· 5 days (Mon-Fri: 9am to 6pm)</p>\n<p>· Job Types: Full-time, Permanent</p>\n<p>· Location : Bukit Batok Connection Building</p>\n<p>· Email : Accounts-SIN@css-shipping.com</p>",
